result.name: More Rounded and Improved Roblox Dark
result.description:
Only for roblox on dark mode

It gives a modern vibe to the roblox web!

This theme includes:
- Rounded frames
- Animated buttons
- Animated game cards
- Blurred side & top bar frame

And more!

If you know something that you think can be animated or improved, then please suggest it in the chat.
result.notes:
- added status rings on homepage!
i will make the profile page status rings later

- improved the friend chat. I hope you like it!

- even better tab design

If you have a idea/problem you can always ask
